OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FA mother's fight for justice continues
OL,7,Fafter her daughter was shot dead by
OL,8,Fher own father ` now her MP plans to
OL,9,Fraise her case in Parliament.
OL,11,FThe investigation into the killing of
OL,12,F23-year-old Lucy Harrison in Texas was
OL,13,F"rushed through", according to
OL,14,FWarrington South MP, who claims the
OL,15,Ffamily has also been failed by the
OL,16,FForeign Office.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@PO]
