OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FLucy, a fashion graduate from
OL,7,FWarrington, was shot through the heart
OL,8,Fby her father, Kris Harrison, at his
OL,9,Fhome in Prosper, Texas, on 10 January
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FHe admitted drinking that day but was
OL,13,Fnever arrested, and a grand jury later
OL,14,Fdecided there was no case to answer.
OL,16,FHowever, a UK coroner ruled in
OL,17,FFebruary 2026 that Lucy's death was
OL,18,Funlawful, concluding the shooting was
OL,19,Freckless after reviewing police
OL,20,Fevidence, witness statements and
OL,21,Fforensic reports.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
