OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FLucy's mother, Jane Coates, says she
OL,7,Fcannot understand how her daughter's
OL,8,Fdeath has led to no consequences.
OL,10,F"How can somebody shoot and kill their
OL,11,Fown daughter and there be no
OL,12,Fconsequences for that?" she said.
OL,13,F"He's still free to go about his life,
OL,14,Fwhile we've been given this life
OL,15,Fsentence."
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@WO]uD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
