OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FLabour MP Sarah Hall is now working
OL,7,Fwith Lucy's family and plans to raise
OL,8,Fthe case in Parliament. She is calling
OL,9,Fon the UK government to put pressure
OL,10,Fon US authorities to reopen the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FHall said evidence suggests Lucy was
OL,14,Fstanding in front of her father when
OL,15,Fthe gun was fired. "There's no other
OL,16,Fway that it could have happened other
OL,17,Fthan him pointing a gun at her," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@TOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
