PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776682974
OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FBody camera footage shows Harrison
OL,7,Finitially told police the gun "just
OL,8,Fwent off" as Lucy stood nearby, but
OL,9,Fher family dispute this account and
OL,10,Fsay she would never have asked to
OL,11,Fhandle the weapon.
OL,13,FThe coroner concluded that firing the
OL,14,Fgun in those circumstances would have
OL,15,Frequired Harrison to point it at his
OL,16,Fdaughter and pull the trigger without
OL,17,Fchecking if it was loaded ` describing
OL,18,Fthe act as reckless.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
