PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776682974
OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FConcerns have also been raised about
OL,7,Fhow the investigation was handled by
OL,8,Fpolice in Texas.
OL,10,FThe MP questioned why Harrison was not
OL,11,Fbreathalysed despite admitting he had
OL,12,Fbeen drinking, and said there appeared
OL,13,Fto be a lack of thorough questioning.
OL,15,FShe also criticised the UK Foreign
OL,16,FOffice, saying Lucy's family were "let
OL,17,Fdown from day one" and given little
OL,18,Fsupport or guidance.
OL,26,@xD@cOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
