OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776682974
OL,3,CMP to raise Texas shooting case in
OL,4,CParliament amid calls for review
OL,6,FMs Coates said officials struggled to
OL,7,Fexplain key parts of the US legal
OL,8,Fsystem and at one stage withdrew
OL,9,Faccess to victim support services.
OL,11,FShe believes more could have been done
OL,12,Fto help the family get answers.
OL,14,FAlthough US authorities have
OL,15,Fjurisdiction over the case, the
OL,16,FForeign Office said it could step in
OL,17,Fwhere cases are highly complex.
OL,18,FDespite this, Coates says no
OL,19,Fmeaningful intervention was made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
